From 67fa2cdf50fd3e5dbc403f446ca7262216a7dd06 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Disyer <daniel@tohka.us>
Date: Thu, 7 May 2026 12:31:28 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] feat: enable open self-registration with optional domain
 restriction

Replace the static "Please contact admin" registration page with a
full registration form (email + password). On success, the user is
automatically logged in and redirected to /project.

Add OVERLEAF_ALLOWED_REGISTRATION_DOMAINS env var to restrict
self-registration to specific email domains (comma-separated).
When unset, registration is open to all domains.
---
